        "content": "This Act may be called the Calcutta High Court (Jurisdictional Limits) Act, 1919.",
        "footnotes": "",
        "query": "abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_3_00030_191915_1523343136342&sectionId=42400&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_3_00030_191915_1523343136342"
